{"tid":2430689,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★美國】著名兒童故事 涉歧視中國人（手拿筷子和碗）和非裔 禁止發行！","createTime":"2021-03-03T06:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T10:33:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dce4d1634b97343903ec7ba32833fd9bbc1c3ed3","tid":2430689,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:02:59.000Z","msg":"已故經典童書作家蘇斯博士（Dr, Seuss）的六本著名童書，因內容涉及對華人和非裔種族歧視及思慮不周的圖像，2日宣布停止發行。其中包括他在1937年出版的第一本童書「我在桑樹街上看到的一切」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n桑樹街一書  描繪華人眼細長手拿筷<br />\n<br />\n「我在桑樹街上看到的一切」一書內容描繪一「Chinaman」（後來在1970年代改成 「Chinese man」）<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>眼睛細長、頭戴尖帽、手拿筷子和飯碗</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121469/5290561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121469%2F5290561&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiulQmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=3aa1f74c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121469/5290561</a>"},{"pid":"b459b66b286ab585b2d20c8c50e39cba7da4cfb1","tid":2430689,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:03:11.000Z","msg":"支拜effect"},{"pid":"30a534a9f9ae2ce3dbaa1973396c2edfe78d7c75","tid":2430689,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ydePkhx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FydePkhx.png&h=db16d029&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34e1d20bcc77425b0d15e0f13247f7496ad287d5","tid":2430689,"uid":204929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"點解咁樣歧視中國人?"},{"pid":"b3906e7b00e9cb4c2a88936f5989cf210c939ffe","tid":2430689,"uid":165113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"chinaman唔係啊蝗嘉爾自稱嚟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a62a85f65f00d8895a25263c04be7479c63ca8","tid":243